casebody.head_matter:
Briand WILLIAMS, petitioner,
v.
CALIFORNIA.
No. 18-8713.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 13, 2019.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, Second Appellate District dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
